# Malik Al Waqt - Software Requirements Specification

## Project Name
Malik Al Waqt

## Version
1.0

## Platform
Android

## Business Type
Luxury E-Commerce

## Products
- Luxury Watches
- Premium Perfumes

## User Roles

### Customer
- Register
- Login
- Browse Products
- Search Products
- Add to Wishlist
- Add to Cart
- Checkout
- Track Orders
- View Order History
- Edit Profile

### Admin
- Dashboard
- Add Products
- Edit Products
- Delete Products
- Manage Orders
- Manage Users
- Manage Coupons
- Sales Reports

## Payment Methods
- Credit/Debit Card
- Bank Transfer
- Cash on Delivery (Optional)

## Notifications
- Order Placed
- Order Shipped
- Order Delivered
- Promotions

## Future Features
- Live Chat
- AI Recommendations
- Multi-language
